        <h3>Headquarters + Backup NOC Overview:</h3>
        <p>Designed with redundancies in place to ensure maximum uptime and accessibility, our corporate headquarters office serves as our backup Network Operations Center. The NOC within our headquarters served as our primary data center facility for twelve years (1998-2010) with a historic uptime of over 99.95%.</p>
